dict.string:
Monday - Upper Power
Barbell Bench Press - 3x3 - 5 Incline DB Bench Press - 3x6 - 10 Bentover Row - 3x3 - 5 Lat Pulldown - 3x6 - 10 Overhead Press - 3x5 - 8 Barbell Curl - 3x6 - 10 Skullcrusher - 3x6 - 10
Tuesday - Lower Power
Squat - 4x3 - 5 Deadlift - 3x3 -5 Leg Press - 3x10 - 15 Leg Curl - 3x6 - 10 Calf Raise - 4x6 - 10
Thursday - Upper Hypertrophy
Incline Barbell Bench Press - 3x8 - 12 Flat Bench DB Fly - 3x8 - 12 Seated Cable Row - 3x8 - 12 One-Arm DB Row - 3x8 - 12 Lateral Raise - 3x8 - 12 Seated Incline DB Curl - 3x8 - 12 Tricep Extension - 3x8 - 12
Friday - Lower Hypertrophy
Front Squat - 3x8 - 12 Barbell Lunge - 3x8 - 12 Leg Extension - 3x10 - 15 Leg Curl - 3x10 - 15 Seated Calf Raise - 3x8 - 12 Calf Press - 3x8 - 12
Instructions:
4 days per week. Rest on Wednesday and weekends.

Push (Chest/Triceps/Shoulders)
Flat Barbell Bench Press - 3x5 Overhead Press - 3x5 Incline Barbell Bench Press - 3x5 Lateral Raise - 3x10 - 12 Rope Pushdown - 3x10 - 12 Overhead DB Extension - 3x10 - 12 Shrugs - 3x10 - 12
Pull (Back/Biceps)
Barbell Row - 3x5 Lat Pulldown - 3x8 - 10 Seated Row - 3x8 - 10 Face Pull - 3x10 - 12 Barbell Bicep Curl - 4x10 - 12 Hammer Curl - 3x10 - 12
Legs (Quad/Hamstring/Calf)
Squat - 4x5 - 6 Leg Press - 3x8 - 10 Leg Extension - 3x10 - 12 Hamstring Curl - 3x10 - 12 Standing Calf Raise - 5x10 - 12
Instructions:
6 days per week. Push/Pull/Legs/REST/Push/Pull/Legs OR Push/Pull/Legs/Push/Pull/Legs/REST

Pull
Deadlift - 1x5+ Barbell Row - 4x5, 1x5+ Pullup - 3x8 - 12 Seated Cable Row - 3x8 - 12 Face Pull - 5x15 - 20 Hammer Curl - 4x8 - 12 Dumbbell Curl - 4x8 - 12
Push
Bench Press 4x5, 1x5+ Overhead Press 3x8 - 12 Incline DB Press - 3x8 - 12 Tricep Pushdown - 3x8 - 12 Lateral Raise - 3x15 - 20 Overhead Tricep Extension - 3x8 - 12
Legs
Squat - 2x5, 1x5+ Romanian Deadlift - 3x8 - 12 Leg Press - 3x8 - 12 Leg Curl - 3x8 - 12 Calf Raise - 5x8 - 12
Instructions:
6 days per week. Push/Pull/Legs/REST/Push/Pull/Legs OR Push/Pull/Legs/Push/Pull/Legs/REST

Monday - Lower
Squat - 3x6 - 8 Leg Curl - 3x6 - 8 Leg Press - 2x10 - 12 Lying Hamstring Curl - 3x10 - 12 Standing Calf Raise - 3x6 - 8 Seated Calf Raise - 2x10 - 12
Tuesday - Upper
Flat Barbell Bench Press - 3x6 - 8 Barbell Row - 3x6 - 8 Incline Bench Press - 3x10 - 12 Overhead Press - 3x10 - 12 Tricep Pushdown - 2x12 - 15 DB Bicep Curl - 2x12 - 15
Thursday - Repeat Lower
Friday - Repeat Upper
Instructions:
4 days per week. Repeat Mon/Tue workouts on Thu/Fri.

Chest and Biceps (A)
Flat Barbell Bench Press - 4x6 - 8 Decline Bench Press - 3x8 - 10 Incline DB Fly - 3x8 - 10 Dumbbell Pullover - 3x8 - 10 Standing Barbell Curl - 4x6 - 8 Preacher Curl - 4x8 - 10
Back and Triceps (A)
Weighted Pullup - 4x8 - 10 Bentover Row - 3x6 - 8 Rack Pull - 3x6 - 8 Hyperextension - 4x10 Tricep Extension - 4x6 - 8 Tricep Pushdown - 4x8 - 10
Shoulders and Legs (A)
Seated Barbell Press - 4x6 - 8 Lateral Raise - 3x8 - 10 Face Pull - 3x10 Barbell Shrug - 4x8 - 10 Squat - 4x6 - 8 Single Hamstring Curl - 4x8 - 10 Standing Calf Raise - 4x10
Chest and Biceps (B)
Incline DB Press - 4x6 - 8 Decline Bench Press - 3x8 - 10 Flat Dumbbell Fly - 3x8 - 10 Dumbbell Pullover - 3x8 - 10 Dumbbell Hammer Curl - 4x6 - 8 Concentration Curl - 4x8 - 10
Back and Triceps (B)
Underhand Grip Pulldown - 4x8 - 10 Seated Cable Row - 3x6 - 8 One-Arm DB Row - 3x6 - 8 Hyperextension - 4x10 Close Grip Bench Press - 4x6 - 8 Skullcrusher - 4x6 - 8
Shoulders and Legs (B)
Seated DB Press - 4x6 - 8 Inverted Row - 4x10 Lateral Cable Raise - 4x10 Dumbell Shrug - 4x8 - 10 Stiff-Legged Deadlift - 4x6 - 8 Machine Hack Squat - 4x8 - 10 Seated Calf Raise - 4x10
Instructions:
6 days per week. Perform A workouts then B workouts. Push/Pull/Legs/REST/Push/Pull/Legs OR Push/Pull/Legs/Push/Pull/Legs/REST
